<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>Login Required Forum</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: sans-serif;
			max-width: 900px;
			margin: 50px auto;
			padding: 20px;
		}
		.error {
			background: #f8d7da;
			color: #721c24;
			padding: 20px;
			border-radius: 8px;
			border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
		}
		a {
			color: #e67e22;
		}
		h2 {
			margin-top: 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="error">
		<h2>⚠️ Login-Required Forum</h2>
		<p>We apologize, but this thread is in a forum that requires a login to access (like the Jo Momma forum).</p>
		<p>Our notification service cannot monitor login-required forums because we don't have access to authenticate as individual users.</p>
		<p><strong>Thread URL:</strong><br>{{.ThreadURL}}</p>
		<p><a href="/">Try a different thread</a></p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
